01:34.567 --> 01:37.067
YOU DON'T NEED
NO TICKET.

01:37.067 --> 01:39.067
OKAY.

01:45.667 --> 01:49.767
( singing 'El-Kelonenu Hebrew )

01:49.800 --> 01:51.767
LARRY.

01:51.800 --> 01:52.800
RABBI.

01:52.833 --> 01:54.667
