02:38.300 --> 02:41.467
IT'S AWFUL.

02:41.500 --> 02:43.433
UPTOWN ?

02:43.467 --> 02:46.300
YEAH, YEAH.

02:46.333 --> 02:51.967
BIKE MESSENGER HIT HIM.

02:52.067 --> 02:55.833
HMM.

02:55.867 --> 02:56.933
WHAT A SHAME.

02:56.967 --> 02:59.700
YEAH, YEAH.

02:59.733 --> 03:02.133
WELL, THAT'S, UH...

03:02.167 --> 03:04.233
YEAH ?
HEY, RABBI ?

03:04.267 --> 03:08.833
UM, CAN I DISCUSS A, UH...

03:08.867 --> 03:10.467
PRIVATE MATTER
WITH YOU ?

03:10.500 --> 03:12.467
PLEASE, ANYTHING,
I'M A RABBI,

03:12.500 --> 03:14.433
