YOU WANT TO SAY.

03:14.467 --> 03:18.100
WELL, 10 YEARS AGO
BEFORE WE GOT MARRIED.

03:18.133 --> 03:22.500
MY WIFE TOLD ME THAT IF WE
STAYED TOGETHER FOR 10 YEARS,

03:22.533 --> 03:27.200
THAT FOR OUR 10th ANNIVERSARY,
AS A PRESENT TO ME,

03:27.233 --> 03:32.167
SHE WOULD LET ME HAVE
RELATIONS WITH ANOTHER WOMAN.

03:32.200 --> 03:33.367
JUST ONE TIME.

03:33.400 --> 03:36.067
AND, THIS IS LIKE,
THIS IS A GIFT TO YOU ?

03:36.067 --> 03:38.600
IT'S, LIKE, I HAVE TOTAL
PERMISSION TO DO IT.

03:38.633 --> 03:39.667
YEAH ?

03:39.700 --> 03:41.433
SHE'S ALMOST KIND OF
CHALLENGING ME IN A WAY.

03:41.467 --> 03:43.400
IN A KIND OF DEMEANING WAY,
SHE DOESN'T THINK I'M,

03:43.433 --> 03:45.100
YOU KNOW,
SUAVE ENOUGH.

03:45.133 --> 03:46.333
OH REALLY ?

03:46.367 --> 03:48.700
AND I WANT TO, IT'S THE ONLY
OPPORTUNITY I'LL EVER HAVE

03:48.733 --> 03:50.433
FOR THE REST
OF MY LIFE.

03:50.467 --> 03:52.800
I'VE NEVER CHEATED ON HER,
I NEVER WOULD CHEAT.

03:52.833 --> 03:54.167
THIS IS ALL
ON THE UP AND UP.

03:54.200 --> 03:55.500
SO YOU'RE CONFLICTED
ABOUT IT ?

03:55.533 --> 03:58.133
YES, YET I KIND OF,
YOU KNOW, I'LL BE HONEST,

03:58.167 --> 03:59.267
IT WOULD BE NICE.

03:59.300 --> 04:02.433
YOU KNOW WHAT COMES
TO MY MIND, LARRY ?

