THE STORY OF ABRAHAM AND SARAH.

04:06.067 --> 04:10.500
SARAH COULD NOT CONCEIVE,
AND SARAH SAID TO ABRAHAM,

04:10.533 --> 04:12.567
YOU KNOW, GO INTO
YOUR HANDMAIDEN,

04:12.600 --> 04:16.267
YOU KNOW, HAGAR,
AND HAVE RELATIONS WITH HER.

04:16.300 --> 04:18.633
