SAID THAT TO HIM ?

04:18.667 --> 04:19.500
YEAH, ABSOLUTELY.

04:19.533 --> 04:20.833
GET THE HELL
OUTTA HERE !

04:20.867 --> 04:22.433
IT'S RIGHT THERE
IN GENESIS.

04:22.467 --> 04:26.833
