04:31.767 --> 04:33.100
SO, I MEAN, THERE'S NO
DANGER OF THAT, RIGHT ?

04:33.133 --> 04:34.433
NO !

04:34.467 --> 04:37.200
IT'S NOT AN ACT OF LOVE
ANYWAY, IT'S LUST.

04:37.233 --> 04:38.533
SO, YOU KNOW...

04:38.567 --> 04:41.300
LOVE, I DON'T KNOW WHAT
THAT HAS TO DO WITH SEX ?

04:41.333 --> 04:43.867
YEAH, WELL IT HAS
A LOT TO DO, BUT...

04:43.900 --> 04:45.367
YEAH, FOR SURE.

04:45.400 --> 04:48.933
I WOULD SAY THAT SHE'S GIVING
YOU SOMETHING OUT OF GENEROSITY

04:48.967 --> 04:51.167
AND I THINK YOU
SHOULD PROBABLY

04:51.200 --> 04:54.600
ACCEPT IT IN THAT
SAME SENSE OF GENEROSITY.

04:54.633 --> 04:56.600
AND I'M NOT A BAD PERSON
IF I DO IT ?

04:56.633 --> 04:58.367
NO, NO, YOU'RE NOT
A BAD PERSON IF YOU DO IT.

04:58.400 --> 05:00.667
WELL, I'M A BAD PERSON ANYWAY,
BUT I'M NOT, UH...

05:00.700 --> 05:01.800
I'M NOT AN EXTRA
BAD PERSON ?

05:01.833 --> 05:06.200
NO, IT DOES NOT MAKE YOU
AN EXTRA BAD PERSON.

05:06.233 --> 05:08.567
I'VE GOT TO START COMING
TO TEMPLE MORE OFTEN.

05:08.600 --> 05:10.933
I'M GLAD I COULD
BE HELPFUL WITH THIS.

05:10.967 --> 05:13.233
THANK YOU,
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

05:13.267 --> 05:14.767
YOU'RE VERY WELCOME,
YOU'RE VERY WELCOME.

05:14.800 --> 05:16.700
AND I'LL SEE YOU
TOMORROW NIGHT FOR DINNER ?

05:16.733 --> 05:17.833
OH YES, I'M LOOKING
FORWARD TO THAT,

05:17.867 --> 05:19.233
OH LISTEN, UM, LARRY,

05:19.267 --> 05:21.333
I WAS TALKING
TO A FRIEND OF MINE,

05:21.367 --> 05:26.467
AND, UH, HE'S A SURVIVOR,
AND HE WOULD LOVE TO MEET YOU.

05:26.500 --> 05:28.767
WOULD IT BE POSSIBLE,
I MEAN...

05:28.800 --> 05:29.667
FOR ME TO BRING HIM
TO DINNER ?

05:29.700 --> 05:30.867
OF COURSE !

05:30.900 --> 05:32.167
I DON'T WANT TO IMPOSE
OR ANYTHING, I MEAN...

05:32.200 --> 05:33.567
THERE'S NO IMPOSITION AT ALL,
YOU WANT A FRIEND OF YOURS,

05:33.600 --> 05:35.067
BRING HIM OVER,
THAT'S FINE.

05:35.067 --> 05:35.933
OH, THAT'S WONDERFUL.

05:35.967 --> 05:37.167
YEAH, IT'S JUST
GONNA BE MY FAMILY,

05:37.200 --> 05:37.967
THAT'S ALL,
IT'S NOT A BIG DEAL.

05:38.067 --> 05:39.267
HE'LL BE
ABSOLUTELY THRILLED.

05:39.300 --> 05:41.300
ALRIGHT.
OKAY.

05:41.333 --> 05:43.900
GO, ENJOY.

05:43.933 --> 05:45.233
RABBI, THANK YOU.

05:45.267 --> 05:46.600
OKAY.

05:49.700 --> 05:51.867
YES, YOUR HONOR, I DO ADMIT,
FOR THE LAST 20 YEARS

05:51.900 --> 05:53.267
I'VE BEEN A LYING,
DOUBLE-CROSSING, TWO-FACED--

05:53.300 --> 05:59.600
( distant shouting )

05:59.633 --> 06:03.600
JUST STOP IT,
I CAN'T STAND IT ANYMORE,
I CAN'T STAND IT !

06:10.833 --> 06:11.967
HOW'S IT GOING ?

06:12.067 --> 06:13.200
IT'S NOT GOING WELL.

06:13.233 --> 06:15.200
I'M TRYING
TO MEMORIZE THIS STUFF,

06:15.233 --> 06:17.300
THEY'RE MAKING
A RACKET.

06:17.333 --> 06:19.067
I'VE GOT TWO WEEKS.

06:19.067 --> 06:21.433
YOU'RE DOING GREAT.

06:21.467 --> 06:22.800
I'M GONNA BE
HUMILIATED.

06:22.833 --> 06:27.900
OH, THE RABBI SAID HE'S
BRINGING A SURVIVOR TOMORROW.

06:27.933 --> 06:29.867
SHOULD I HAVE MY FATHER
BRING HIS FRIEND, SOLLY ?

06:29.900 --> 06:31.767
WHO'S ALSO A SURVIVOR.

06:31.800 --> 06:33.067
YOU KNOW, THE GUY
WITH THE GLASS EYE.

06:33.067 --> 06:33.833
OH, RIGHT.

06:33.867 --> 06:34.967
YEAH.
REMEMBER HIM ?

06:35.067 --> 06:36.500
YOU THINK THAT'S
A GOOD IDEA ?

06:36.533 --> 06:38.967
DO SURVIVORS LIKE
SEEING EACH OTHER ?

06:39.067 --> 06:41.500
DO THEY LIKE TO TALK
ABOUT OLD TIMES OR...

06:41.533 --> 06:44.500
DOES THE SIGHT OF ANOTHER
SURVIVOR DEPRESS THEM ?

06:44.533 --> 06:46.233
I THINK YOU
SHOULD INVITE HIM.

06:46.267 --> 06:47.167
INVITE HIM.

06:47.200 --> 06:48.200
I GUESS IF
I WAS A SURVIVOR,

06:48.233 --> 06:49.600
I'D WANT TO SEE SOMEBODY,
YOU KNOW...

06:49.633 --> 06:51.167
YOU WANT TO SEE SOMEBODY,
YOU HAVE A SHARED EXPERIENCE.

06:51.200 --> 06:54.400
YEAH, TALK ABOUT,
WELL, SEE THAT'S THE THING.

06:54.433 --> 06:56.700
DO THEY WANT TO--
I DON'T KNOW.

06:56.733 --> 07:00.100
HOW ARE YOUR VOWS
COMING ALONG ?

07:00.133 --> 07:03.733
I JUST HAVEN'T HAD THAT MUCH
TIME TO REALLY WORK ON IT YET.

07:03.767 --> 07:05.100
THIS IS IMPORTANT
TO ME, LARRY.

07:05.133 --> 07:06.700
HE WHOLE THING'S GONNA
BE EMBARRASSING ANYWAY,

07:06.733 --> 07:08.300
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
THIS WAS GONNA BE PART
OF THE WHOLE THING,

07:08.333 --> 07:09.700
THAT I WAS GONNA HAVE TO SAY
THIS IN FRONT OF PEOPLE,

07:09.733 --> 07:10.567
I THOUGHT IT WAS...

07:10.600 --> 07:14.533
OKAY, I'M GIVING
YOU A GOOD GIFT.

07:14.567 --> 07:16.233
OKAY.

07:16.267 --> 07:19.233
SO THIS IS WHAT
I HAVE SO FAR.

07:19.267 --> 07:22.433
"MAY I ALWAYS HAVE THE WISDOM
TO LOOK PAST YOUR SHORT COMINGS

07:22.467 --> 07:25.200
"AND APPRECIATE ALL OF
THE GOODNESS YOU POSSESS.

07:25.233 --> 07:29.467
"WE, PROMISE TO CONTINUE LOVING
EACH OTHER UNCONDITIONALLY.

07:29.500 --> 07:31.733
"NOT ONLY THROUGHOUT
THIS LIFETIME,

07:31.767 --> 07:34.233
"BUT AFTER DEATH
THROUGH ALL ETERNITY.

07:34.267 --> 07:35.733
"WE STAND BEFORE YOU--

07:35.767 --> 07:39.067
HUH, WAIT A SECOND.

07:39.067 --> 07:40.667
WHAT ?

07:40.700 --> 07:42.233
WHAT WAS THAT
ABOUT ETERNITY ?

07:42.267 --> 07:46.700
UM, "WE'LL LOVE EACH OTHER,
THROUGHOUT THIS LIFE TIME,

07:46.733 --> 07:48.467
BUT AFTER DEATH
THROUGH ALL ETERNITY."

07:48.500 --> 07:52.333
YOU MEAN THIS IS...

07:52.367 --> 07:56.600
THIS IS CONTINUING
INTO THE AFTERLIFE ?

07:56.633 --> 07:58.867
YEAH, THAT'S THE IDEA.

07:58.900 --> 08:00.767
DO YOU HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT ?

08:00.800 --> 08:05.333
WELL, I...

08:05.367 --> 08:07.100
I THOUGHT THIS
WAS OVER AT DEATH.

08:07.133 --> 08:10.500
I DIDN'T KNOW WE WENT
INTO ETERNITY TOGETHER.

08:10.533 --> 08:13.333
I, UH, ISN'T THAT
WHAT IT SAID IN...

08:13.367 --> 08:14.833
'TILL DEATH DO US PART,
I THOUGHT IT WAS...

08:14.867 --> 08:16.233
DO YOU HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH ETERNITY ?!

08:16.267 --> 08:17.267
WELL.

08:17.300 --> 08:19.400
WE FINALLY FOUND
EACH OTHER, LARRY,

08:19.433 --> 08:22.567
AND WE'RE CELEBRATING THIS
FOR ALL ETERNITY.

08:22.600 --> 08:26.667
I GUESS I HAD A DIFFERENT
PLAN FOR ETERNITY, I THOUGHT...

08:26.700 --> 08:29.733
I THOUGHT I'D BE SINGLE,
I GUESS.

08:29.767 --> 08:34.733
I'M SORRY, I'M INTERRUPTING
YOUR SINGLE LIFE IN ETERNITY ?

08:34.767 --> 08:37.800
NO, I JUST DIDN'T
REALIZE THAT...

08:37.833 --> 08:41.500
THIS RELATIONSHIP CARRIED
OVER AFTER DEATH, THAT--

08:41.533 --> 08:44.067
WELL, IT DOES,
IT CARRIES OVER !

08:44.067 --> 08:45.200
SO I GUESS I JUST
TOOK THAT FOR GRANTED.

08:45.233 --> 08:48.767
OKAY, DO YOU NOT WANT
TO RENEW OUR VOWS, BECAUSE--

08:48.800 --> 08:52.467
NO, I WANT TO RENEW OUR VOWS
UNTIL, YOU KNOW, I DIDN'T--

08:52.500 --> 08:55.300
CAN WE TAKE OUT
THE ETERNITY PART ?

08:55.333 --> 08:57.067
NO.

09:02.467 --> 09:03.233
OKAY.

09:09.167 --> 09:11.233
( Cheryl )
NICE MEETING YOU.

09:11.267 --> 09:13.900
THIS IS A TREAT,
THIS IS REALLY A TREAT.

09:13.933 --> 09:14.967
THE TREAT IS OURS.

09:15.067 --> 09:16.767
HI.

09:16.800 --> 09:19.167
LOOK AT YOU,
YOU LOOK GREAT.

09:19.200 --> 09:19.867
YOU HAPPY ?

09:19.900 --> 09:21.133
YEAH, I'M VERY HAPPY.

09:21.167 --> 09:22.967
DID I REALLY NEED TO WEAR
A SUIT FOR THIS, HUH ?

09:23.067 --> 09:25.233
YES, LOOK AT EVERYBODY
