09:26.767 --> 09:29.767
OH YEAH, YOU SHOULD
SAY HELLO TO THE RABBI,

09:29.800 --> 09:32.600
6AND, YOU KNOW,
MIX AND MINGLE WITH PEOPLE.

09:32.633 --> 09:33.800
LARRY.

09:33.833 --> 09:35.300
HELLO RABBI.

09:35.333 --> 09:36.367
HELLO.
HELLO.

09:36.400 --> 09:37.800
THIS IS COLBY.

09:37.833 --> 09:42.200
HI, LARRY,
NICE TO MEET YOU.

09:42.233 --> 09:44.800
WHERE IS THIS SURVIVOR ?

09:44.833 --> 09:48.633
WHAT--
HE'S THE SURVIVOR.

09:48.667 --> 09:51.733
FROM THE--
FROM THE TELEVISION SHOW.

09:51.767 --> 09:52.600
"SURVIVOR."

09:52.633 --> 09:54.133
I WAS OVER
IN AUSTRALIA.

09:54.167 --> 09:55.967
I'M A HUGE FAN
OF "SEINFELD."

09:56.067 --> 09:57.367
HE REALLY IS.

09:57.400 --> 10:00.433
