10:00.467 --> 10:01.333
HE'S GOOD.

10:01.367 --> 10:02.133
YEAH ?

10:02.167 --> 10:05.167
IS HE STILL
DOING STAND UP ?

10:05.200 --> 10:06.733
I JUST THOUGHT YOU TWO
SHOULD MEET, YOU KNOW,

10:06.767 --> 10:07.967
FELLOW CELEBRITIES,
I THOUGHT.

10:08.000 --> 10:09.267
UH-HUH.

10:09.300 --> 10:12.333
THANKS AGAIN,
FOR HAVING ME OVER.

10:12.367 --> 10:15.800
NO PROBLEM.

10:15.833 --> 10:18.100
OKAY, I'M GONNA, UH,
SAY HELLO TO MY DAD.

10:18.133 --> 10:19.233
OKAY.

10:19.267 --> 10:20.367
THANKS AGAIN.

10:20.400 --> 10:21.500
