KEEP MY FATHER COMPANY.

10:48.467 --> 10:51.633
OH, THANK YOU,
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

10:51.667 --> 10:58.567
LISTEN, WHERE IS
THE OTHER SURVIVOR ?

10:58.600 --> 11:03.133
HE'S THAT, UH,
TALL GUY OVER THERE.

11:03.167 --> 11:08.867
HE'S FROM
THE TELEVISION SHOW.

11:08.900 --> 11:11.967
"SURVIVOR" ?

11:12.067 --> 11:14.833
