11:14.867 --> 11:17.233
SO HERE WE ARE IN A REGION
OF AUSTRALIA WHERE,

11:17.267 --> 11:19.500
OUT OF THE WORLD'S
10 MOST DEADLY SNAKES,

11:19.533 --> 11:21.967
NINE OF THEM
INHABIT THIS REGION.

11:22.067 --> 11:23.100
IT WAS HARROWING.

11:23.133 --> 11:25.067
