THE 10th ANNIVERSARY PRESENT,

16:19.367 --> 16:21.300
ALL THAT,
ONE TIME, IT'S ON.

16:21.333 --> 16:22.733
WOW !

16:22.767 --> 16:23.500
GREAT !

16:23.533 --> 16:24.133
AND GUESS WHAT ?

16:24.167 --> 16:24.967
WHAT ?

16:25.067 --> 16:26.600
I'VE GOT
THE RABBI'S BLESSING.

16:26.633 --> 16:28.067
YOU TALKED TO
THE RABBI ABOUT THIS ?

16:28.100 --> 16:30.100
