YES.
REALLY ?

16:42.233 --> 16:43.600
HEY, SUZIE.

16:43.633 --> 16:44.867
YOU FORGOT THE CANTALOUPES,
WHERE ARE THE CANTALOUPES ?

16:44.900 --> 16:46.467
OH, FORGET THE CANTALOUPE,
COME HERE FOR ONE SECOND.

16:46.500 --> 16:49.067
COME HERE,
COME HERE, COME HERE.

16:49.100 --> 16:50.133
HOW DO THE HASSIDS
MAKE LOVE ?

16:50.167 --> 16:51.233
