IT WAS A MYTH.

17:01.767 --> 17:03.433
NO, IT'S NOT A MYTH,
THEY CUT A HOLE IN THE SHEET,

17:03.467 --> 17:06.700
THE MAN PUTS THE PENIS IN, THEY
CAN'T TOUCH EACH OTHER, LARRY.

17:06.733 --> 17:08.600
