THING THAT THEY DO.

17:08.633 --> 17:10.267
WHAT DO YOU GUYS TALK ABOUT,
THIS IS WHAT YOU TALK ABOUT ?

17:10.300 --> 17:11.500
HOW HASSIDS HAVE SEX ?

17:11.533 --> 17:13.300
NO, IT JUST CAME,
THE SUBJECT CAME UP,
IT CAME UP.

17:13.333 --> 17:16.400
HELP ME WITH
THE BAGS, ALRIGHT.

17:16.433 --> 17:17.167
WOW.

17:17.200 --> 17:18.433
YEAH.

17:18.467 --> 17:21.067
HOW DO YOU LIKE THAT,
OH, WELL I GOTTA GET A SHEET.

17:21.100 --> 17:22.067
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT
YOU SHOULD DO,

17:22.100 --> 17:23.800
