FOR A SATIN SHEET.

17:23.833 --> 17:25.200
REALLY, I DON'T THINK
THAT WILL BE GOOD.

17:25.233 --> 17:26.600
I'LL BE SLIDING
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

17:26.633 --> 17:28.067
WELL.

17:28.067 --> 17:29.633
CUT IT BEFORE HAND,
YOU THINK ?

17:29.667 --> 17:31.100
BEFORE HAND, SHOW UP
WITH THE HOLE BEFORE HAND,

17:31.133 --> 17:32.133
YOU GOTTA DO THAT.

17:32.167 --> 17:33.833
