17:38.600 --> 17:39.133
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

17:39.167 --> 17:40.667
ALRIGHT, BYE.

17:44.933 --> 17:47.533
LARRY.

17:47.567 --> 17:49.933
LOOK, HUH, AREN'T YOU
GLAD I PICKED IT UP ?

