TO APOLOGIZE ABOUT THE, UH,

18:20.667 --> 18:24.667
YOU KNOW, THE WHOLE
SPONGE THING.

18:24.700 --> 18:26.400
( clearing throat )

18:26.433 --> 18:29.367
