THAT NIGHT, UH...

18:29.400 --> 18:33.733
BECAUSE OF THE WHOLE,
THE SURVIVOR CONFRONTATION,

18:33.767 --> 18:38.300
IT JUST BROUGHT UP A LOT
OF STUFF ABOUT THE HOLOCAUST,

18:38.333 --> 18:42.333
AND IT'S KIND OF IN MY DNA
AND I WAS VERY FLUMMOXED BY IT.

18:42.367 --> 18:43.767
VERY FLUMMOXED.

18:43.800 --> 18:47.800
YOU WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND,
BUT IF YOU WERE IN MY RELIGION,

18:47.833 --> 18:50.067
WHAT HAPPENED
TO MY PEOPLE,

18:50.100 --> 18:52.067
THINGS CAME OUT THAT
SHOULDN'T HAVE BEEN SAID.

18:52.100 --> 18:56.900
AND, UM, I CERTAINLY
APOLOGIZE FOR THAT.

18:56.933 --> 18:58.067
THANK YOU.

18:58.100 --> 19:03.967
AND, EVEN THOUGH, YOU KNOW,
YOU WERE KIND OF...

