IT'S SO SILLY, COME ON.

19:32.433 --> 19:36.067
A SPONGE,
YES, COME ON.

19:36.067 --> 19:37.067
NEXT TIME YOU'RE
STANDING BY THE KITCHEN...

19:37.067 --> 19:38.333
GET OUT,
I'LL GO GET MY DRESS.

19:38.367 --> 19:39.400
YOU'LL GET A SPONGE.

19:39.433 --> 19:41.067
