20:32.467 --> 20:34.200
YOU, YOU GO
MAKE FUN FOR ME ?

20:34.233 --> 20:35.633
NO, NO, NO.

20:35.667 --> 20:39.633
I DON'T LIKE THIS HERE, I DON'T
WANT TO BE HERE, NO MORE.

20:39.667 --> 20:41.900
HOLD IT,
STOP THE CAR !

20:41.933 --> 20:43.567
NO, SOLLY,
WAIT, SOLLY.

20:43.600 --> 20:46.433
WAIT, SOLLY, PLEASE,
DON'T, DON'T GET UP.

20:46.467 --> 20:48.900
SOMEBODY GET A SPONGE.

20:54.467 --> 20:58.200
( shouting )

20:58.233 --> 21:01.367
RIGHT, SO THEN, I'LL, UH,
DO THE BLESSING,

21:01.400 --> 21:03.900
UH, THE LAST BLESSING.

21:03.933 --> 21:05.700
JUST A LITTLE BIT
OF HEBREW,

21:05.733 --> 21:08.933
AND THEN I WILL PUT
THE GLASS ON THE FLOOR

21:08.967 --> 21:12.067
AND YOU'LL STEP ON IT
AND THAT'LL BE IT.

21:12.067 --> 21:14.067
