MAZEL TOV, PLEASE ?

21:22.067 --> 21:23.133
ANYTHING ELSE, UH ?

21:23.167 --> 21:24.433
UM, JUST THAT THE HEBREW,

21:24.467 --> 21:27.167
I MEAN, ARE WE GONNA
KNOW WHAT YOU'RE SAYING ?

21:27.200 --> 21:28.833
YEAH, I'LL TRANSLATE IT,
THIS IS VERY BASIC.

21:28.867 --> 21:30.067
YOU WANT ME
TO TRANSLATE FOR YOU ?

21:30.067 --> 21:31.733
WE LOVE GOD,
GOD, THANK YOU GOD,

21:31.767 --> 21:35.067
THANKS GOD, GOD YOU'RE GREAT,
OH GOD, OH YOU'RE WONDERFUL,

21:35.067 --> 21:37.100
YOU'RE AMAZING GOD,
IT'S ALL GOD.

21:37.133 --> 21:38.433
IT'S A LITTLE
OVERDONE, BUT.

21:38.467 --> 21:42.933
WELL, IT'S A BLESSING,
IT'S MORE ABOUT YOU THAN GOD.

21:42.967 --> 21:44.667
LARRY, I'M SORRY, UM...

21:44.700 --> 21:47.600
YOU KNOW I DON'T WANT
TO CHANGE THE SUBJECT,

21:47.633 --> 21:49.267
BUT ISN'T THERE SOMETHING
YOU CAN DO ABOUT THAT STAIN ?

21:49.300 --> 21:52.133
I MEAN,
IT'S HORRIFYING.

21:52.167 --> 21:54.167
YEAH, YEAH,
I KNOW IT'S A, UH,

21:54.200 --> 21:56.733
IT'S A GO HOME STAIN,
BUT I DIDN'T GO HOME.

21:56.767 --> 21:59.400
I MEAN, I JUST, IT'S KIND OF
DISRESPECTFUL, YOU KNOW ?

21:59.433 --> 22:03.700
JUST IN TERMS OF STANDING
IN FRONT OF THE ARC AND...

