I GOT A MINT,
IT'S IN MY POCKET.

22:09.633 --> 22:11.167
DO YOU WANT ME
TO HAND IT TO YOU ?

22:11.200 --> 22:13.067
IT'S LOOSE,
IT'S NOT IN A PACKAGE.

22:13.067 --> 22:14.500
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO PUT
YOUR HAND IN MY POCKET

22:14.533 --> 22:16.067
AND GET IT YOURSELF.

22:16.100 --> 22:17.333
YOU GOT THREE OPTIONS,

22:17.367 --> 22:19.733
